description:
Moviefone is the ultimate app for movie showtimes, trailers, reviews, exclusive movie clips and news.

KEY FEATURES:

• "What's New on Moviefone" news carousel
• Get movie details, showtimes, news, and reviews
• Save your favorite theaters for quick and easy access to showtimes
• Buy tickets on the go to any of our participating theaters
• Find theaters easily with our maps and directions feature
• Find places to eat or grab a drink near any theater
• View movies in theaters, top box office hits, coming soon and new on DVD
• Watch high quality trailers and movie clips in full screen 
• Share movie details on Facebook, Twitter, SMS or by email
• Get the latest news for all your favorite movies and actors
• Search movies to find the perfect movie for the kids or date night 
• Search movies by title or actor 
• Use AirPlay to steam videos to your Apple TV

We hope you love the app as much as we do. As always, we appreciate your feedback so keep sending them to moviefone.ipad.fb@teamaol.com.
